dmca.title: Copyright Infringement Notification - cutiecentral.com FA-R292
dmca.body:
EN

 

-----Original Message-----
From: Richard Kawasaki [mailto:richardk@baytsp.com] 
Sent: Tuesday, October 19, 2004 7:21 PM
To: hostmaster@globat.com; abuse@mzima.net; support@cutiecentral.com;
webmaster@imageshack.us; copyright@theplanet.com
Cc: feinarts@aol.com
Subject: Copyright Infringement Notification - cutiecentral.com FA-R292

 

Dear Sirs: 
We would like to request that the subsciber responsible for the infringements below
be banned from using your site, in order to ensure that such egregious violations of
copyright law are not repeated. Thank you for your cooperation.

Robert Fein Photography/Fein Arts Internet has authorized BayTSP.com to act as its
agent for copyright infringement notification. The spidering of the Web has detected
infringements on your website as detailed in the report below. Therefore, this
letter is an official notification under the provisions of section 512(c) of the
Digital Millennium Copyright Act to effect removal of the detected infringements
listed in the attached report. The Berne Convention for the Protection of Literary
and Artistic Works, the Universal Copyright Convention, as well as bilateral
treaties with other countries allow for protection of our client's images even
beyond US borders. The documentation below specifies the exact location of the
infringement. The BayFile ID identifies our images by shoot number. We hereby
request that you immediately remove the offending material, as specified in RFC
1036, and refrain from using our client's materials in the future. 

BayTSP.com has a good faith belief that use of the material in the manner complained
of in the attached report, is not authorized by Robert Fein Photography/Fein Arts
Internet, its agent, or the law. The information provided herein is accurate to the
best of our knowledge. 

BayTSP.com hereby swears under penalty of perjury that BayTSP.com is authorized to
act on behalf of Robert Fein Photography/Fein Arts Internet for matters pertaining
to notification of infringement of its exclusive rights in its copyrighted material.


Please send us a prompt response indicating the actions you have taken to resolve
this matter. Please reference BayTSP Notification ID in your response. 

Sincerely,
Richard Kawasaki
Compliance Manager
BayTSP.com
PO Box 1314
Los Gatos, CA 95031-1314
(408) 341-2300
dmca@baytsp.com
